---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';

const lastUpdated = "March 2026"; // Update this to the current date
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy | Heath Court Ltd">

  <main class="bg-slate-50 py-16 px-4">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto bg-white shadow-sm border border-slate-200 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden">
      
      <!-- Header -->
      <div class="bg-slate-900 p-8 md:p-12 text-white text-center">
        <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold mb-4 tracking-tight">Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p class="text-slate-400">Last Updated: {lastUpdated}</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Content -->
      <div class="p-8 md:p-12 text-slate-700 leading-relaxed space-y-8">
        
        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4 border-b pb-2">1. Introduction</h2>
          <p>
            Heath Court Ltd ("we", "our", or "us") is committed to protecting and respecting your privacy. This policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your personal data when you visit our website or interact with our wholesale services. 
            We are a company registered in England (Address: Unit A 82 James Carter Road, Mildenhall, IP28 7DE).
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4 border-b pb-2">2. Information We Collect</h2>
          <p class="mb-4">We may collect and process the following data about you:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
            <li><strong>Identity Data:</strong> Name, job title, and company name.</li>
            <li><strong>Contact Data:</strong> Email address, phone number, and business billing/delivery address.</li>
            <li><strong>Technical Data:</strong> IP address, browser type, and location data when visiting our website.</li>
            <li><strong>Inquiry Data:</strong> Information provided when you request a wholesale quote or price list.</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4 border-b pb-2">3. How We Use Your Data</h2>
          <p class="mb-4">We use information held about you in the following ways:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
            <li>To provide you with wholesale pricing and product catalogs.</li>
            <li>To process orders and manage your trade account.</li>
            <li>To notify you about changes to our services or inventory.</li>
            <li>To comply with legal and tax obligations in the UK.</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4 border-b pb-2">4. Data Security</h2>
          <p>
            We have put in place appropriate security measures to prevent your personal data from being accidentally lost, used, or accessed in an unauthorised way. Access to your personal data is limited to employees and third parties who have a business need to know.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4 border-b pb-2">5. Disclosure of Your Information</h2>
          <p>
            We do not sell your data. We may share your information with selected third parties including delivery couriers to fulfill your orders and professional service providers (accountants/auditors) as required by law.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4 border-b pb-2">6. Your Rights (GDPR)</h2>
          <p class="mb-4">Under the UK GDPR, you have the following rights:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
            <li><strong>Access:</strong> Request a copy of the personal data we hold about you.</li>
            <li><strong>Correction:</strong> Request that we correct any inaccurate information.</li>
            <li><strong>Erasure:</strong> Request that we delete your personal data.</li>
            <li><strong>Object:</strong> Object to the processing of your data for marketing purposes.</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="bg-blue-50 p-6 rounded-xl border border-blue-100">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-blue-900 mb-4">7. Contact Us</h2>
          <p class="mb-4 text-blue-800">
            If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy or our data practices, please contact us at:
          </p>
          <ul class="text-blue-900 text-sm space-y-1">
            <li><strong>Email:</strong> info@heathcourtltd.com</li>
            <li><strong>Address:</strong> Unit A 82 James Carter Road, Mildenhall, Bury St. Edmunds, IP28 7DE</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

      </div>
    </div>
  </main>


</Layout>